column5: does anyone have any info they are willing to share on good walleye lakes near sioux lookout (with in 30 - 40 miles) drive in only with a public landing. looking for a day trip. have a cabin on minnitaki and am looking to branch out and fish some different water. there is so much up there though i don't know where to start. could trade some good info for eyes,trout, or pike on minnitaki. scar
